CompileScript: <<
<<
InstallScript: <<
mkdir -p %i/share/texmf.local/tex/chess
mkdir -p %i/share/texmf.local/fonts/tfm/public/chess/
mkdir -p %i/share/texmf.local/fonts/source/public/chess/
mkdir -p %i/share/doc/%n/tex/
install -m 644 inputs/chess.sty %i/share/texmf.local/tex/chess/
install -m 644 fonts/*.tfm %i/share/texmf.local/fonts/tfm/public/chess/
install -m 644 mf/chess*mf %i/share/texmf.local/fonts/source/public/chess/
install -m 644 doc/* %i/share/doc/%n/tex/
<<
DocFiles: changes12 copyright readme
License: OSI-Approved
PostInstScript: <<
if [ -f %p/bin/mktexlsr ]; then mktexlsr %p/share/texmf.local; fi
<<
PreRmScript: <<
if [ -f %p/bin/mktexlsr ]; then mktexlsr %p/share/texmf.local; fi
<<
